OL,4,Cpresenter Sandy Gall dies aged 97
OL,6,FJournalist Sandy Gall has been praised
OL,7,Fas a "giant and a gentleman" after his
OL,8,Fdeath at the age of 97.
OL,10,FHis journalism career spanned more
OL,11,Fthan 50 years and he was a renowned
OL,12,Fforeign correspondent for ITN and the
OL,13,Fface of ITV's News At Ten from 1963
OL,14,Funtil 1992.
OL,16,FHis family revealed that he died at
OL,17,Fhis home in Kent on Sunday, and said:
OL,18,F"His was a great life, generously and
OL,19,Fcourageously lived."
