OL,6,FGall covered major events such as the
OL,7,Fassassination of US president John F
OL,8,FKennedy, the civil rights movement and
OL,9,Fthe Lockerbie disaster, after entering
OL,10,Fjournalism as a reporter for the
OL,11,FAberdeen Press and Journal in 1952.
OL,13,FTom Bradby, lead anchor of News At
OL,14,FTen, said: "He had, as a foreign
OL,15,Fcorrespondent, been there and done
OL,16,Feverything.
OL,18,F"As a trainee walking through the
OL,19,Fdoors of ITN 35 years ago, I was one
OL,20,Fof many young would-be reporters he
OL,21,Finspired.
