OL,6,F"His old-world charm and on-screen
OL,7,Fpresence endeared him to so many
OL,8,Fviewers and so many of us.
OL,10,F"He was a giant and a gentleman of our
OL,11,Fbusiness. Everyone loved Sandy."
OL,13,FSir Trevor McDonald, former News At
OL,14,FTen presenter, said: "I think Sandy
OL,15,FGall was one of the most brilliant
OL,16,Fjournalists out there.
OL,18,F"And, around his work, ITN was able to
OL,19,Fbuild an enormous reputation.
