OL,6,F"He travelled the world, he covered
OL,7,Fwars, he covered political upheavals,
OL,8,Fand what he said, people believed.
OL,10,F"He gave ITN and News At Ten its
OL,11,Fcredibility. When Sandy Gall said
OL,12,Fsomething, everyone believed it."
OL,14,FDuring his time as a foreign
OL,15,Fcorrespondent, Gall covered the
OL,16,Farrival of the US into the Vietnam War
OL,17,Fin 1965, and the end of the conflict
OL,18,Fwhen the North Vietnamese army entered
OL,19,FSaigon in 1975.
