OL,4,Cpresenter Sandy Gall dies aged 97
OL,6,FHe was made a CBE in 1987 and
OL,7,FCompanion of the Order of St Michael
OL,8,Fand St George in 2011.
OL,10,FTom Tugendhat MP said: "Quite simply,
OL,11,Fa hero.
OL,13,F"Sandy Gall told the stories we needed
OL,14,Fto hear and kept up with those whose
OL,15,Flives he had brought to our notice.
OL,17,F"My condolences go to Carlotta Gall
OL,18,Fand the whole family. He was a legend
OL,19,Fto many, and a father to a lucky few."
